  <summary date="2023-07-05T10:54:46Z" status="Introduced in House">Responsible Firearms Marketing Act

This bill requires the Federal Trade Commission to study and report on potentially unfair or deceptive practices that may be prevalent in the advertising or marketing of firearms.

Additionally, the commission must issue regulations prohibiting such practices, and the bill provides for enforcement by the commission.</summary>
